#: app/templates/admin/index.html:43
msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Torohevitra ho an'ny Admin"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:45
msgid ""
"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Aza mihazakazaka mihitsy amin'ny famokarana miaraka amin'ny DEBUG alefa. Ny "
"fomba Debug dia mampiseho ny antsipiriany anatiny sy ny stack traces."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Ataovy hatrany ny Grylli aoriana amin'ny proxy miverina (ohatra, Caddy, "
"Nginx, na Traefik) ary ampidiro azy amin'ny alalan'ny HTTPS. Tokony "
"hohamaivanin'ny fivorian'ny angon-drakitra mpampiasa ny ankapobeny."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr ""
"Ataovy azo antoka fa voavotra ao amin'ny mpampiantrano ny lahatahiry data "
"(database)"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"An'ny mpampiasa rehetra ny lahatahiry fitehirizana rakitra mampiakatra. "
"Amin’ny endrika fikandrana ny haterina isaky ny mpampiasa, mamaritra ny "
"lahatahiry sy ny fifehezana fidirana eo amin’ny hatezerana."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"Mba hamerenana indray ny backup: ajanony ny container, soloina ny "
"data/grylli.db izay misy ao amin'ny lahatahiry backups, ary avereno indray "
"ny container."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"Tsy afaka manala ny andraikitry ny mpandrindra ny mpandrindra mba hisorohana"
" ny fanakatonana tsy nahy ny maha-mpandrindra azy ireo."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
msgid ""
"Rate limits and automatic account lockouts are enforced to protect against "
"brute-force login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Atolotra ny fetra ho an'ny taha sy ny fanakatonana mandeha ho azy ny kaonty "
"mba hiarovana amin'ny fanandramana hisoratana anarana malaky sy mamo."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:60
msgid ""
"Passwords, SMTP credentials, and API tokens are encrypted at rest using "
"Fernet."
msgstr ""
"Ny tenimiafina, ny fianimbana SMTP ary ny hydrogen API dia voaaro rehefa "
"miato amin'ny alalàn'i Fernet."

